pageProduct.name: Sukin Brightening Iluminating Eye Gel Tube 15ml
pageProduct.description:
Â 

General Information

With Antioxidant Rich Green Coffee And Kakadu Plum To Help Reduce Dark Circles And Puffiness.

Warnings

Avoid Contact With Eyes. If Irritation Occurs Rinse Immediately And Discontinue Use. For External Use Only.

Common Uses

Refresh And Illuminate The Eye Area With Our Brightening Eye Gel. Formulated With Green Coffee And Kakadu Plum To Reduce The Appearance Of Dark Circles And Brighten The Eye Area.

Ingredients

Ingredients: Water (Aqua), Glycerin, Hydroxyethylcellulose, Terminalia Ferdinandiana Fruit Extract (Kakadu Plum), Caffeine, Coffea Arabica (Coffee) Seed Extract, Ananas Sativus (Pineapple) Fruit Extract, Carthamus Tinctorius (Safflower) Extract, Squalane, Coconut Alkanes, Cetearyl Olivate, Sorbitan Olivate, Coco-Caprylate/Caprate, Xanthan Gum, Lecithin, Citric Acid, Phenoxyethanol, Benzyl Alcohol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate

Directions

Use The Tip Of The Tube To Gently Apply To The Eye Area, Glide From Under Eye Toward Outer Corner And Across Brow Bone. Gently Pat Around Eye Area Using Ring Finger.
